snippet.title: Minecraft: Antichamber Mod Teaser
snippet.description:
A small teaser on the Antichamber Mod for Minecraft. The mod is still a WIP and will be released when it's ready.

UPDATE: Some of you doubt that this is really Minecraft. Here, have an album full of screenshots. http://imgur.com/a/Nwpjx

Many thanks to all the people who have contributed and are currently contributing to this mod.

- Demruth (Alexander Bruce) - For making Antichamber, also an all round nice guy who allowed me to continue working on this mod. Go check out his game (seriously)! 
http://store.steampowered.com/app/219890
http://www.antichamber-game.com/

- Mr_hazard - Matter Gun (mc) design - https://twitter.com/Damien_hazard

- Punchaface - Sounds FX - https://soundcloud.com/punchaface

- Lokidarkfire - Sign Art - https://www.youtube.com/user/LokiKeanu

- aginsun - That guy in the tiny SMP scene.

The build team, with you guys the map would never be at where it's at now.
- WoWAsshi (lead level design)
- Mj11jM
- Malqua
- TheMattaBase
- Alphamine19
- iPixeli
- Necrogami

BGM is "Wasteland" by Punchaface. Used with permission.

==============================

Follow me on Twitter! https://twitter.com/ohaiiChun
